        <h2>Course Description</h2>
        <p>
            The course introduces theories and techniques of language technology and natural language processing. It
            attempts to cover the whole field from speech recognition and synthesis to semantics and dialogue.
        </p>
        <p>It focuses on industrial or laboratory applications, such as document retrieval on the internet, information
            extraction, conversational agents, and verbal interaction in virtual worlds. Fundamental algorithms will be
            described using Python or Perl's regular expressions.
        </p>
