        <h2>Passing the Course</h2>
        <p>To pass the course, you must carry out and validate all the programming assignments and hand in all the
            individual lab reports. You will then obtain a mark of 3. You can sit the optional examination to improve
            your mark to a 4 or a 5.
        </p>
